thread.title: john and chris
thread.title_full: Ace Rental Cars Australia & New Zealand reviewed by john and chris

author: john and chris
title: john and chris
text: Great car that we had,we chose the older version toyota,it ran like a charm,no problems,would choose this car over the new ones any day,plenty of room ,great boot size.staff were pleasant and great free shuttle service.thankyou.will use your company again and i reccomend you to others as well.
